1
00:00:22,464 --> 00:00:26,432
♪Should we forget yesterday's sorrows♪

2
00:00:26,432 --> 00:00:29,728
♪And the dazed confusion♪

3
00:00:30,976 --> 00:00:33,681
♪Should we let go of♪

4
00:00:33,681 --> 00:00:35,904
♪The stubborn madness♪

5
00:00:35,904 --> 00:00:39,072
♪And naive recklessness now♪

6
00:00:40,192 --> 00:00:43,840
♪Those years, those faces♪

7
00:00:44,992 --> 00:00:48,763
♪Those old scars we can't erase♪

8
00:00:49,824 --> 00:00:52,460
♪Tears streaming, facing the light♪

9
00:00:53,152 --> 00:00:57,594
♪Piercing the sorrow within♪

10
00:01:08,716 --> 00:01:12,736
♪The road ahead's long,
stumbling all the way♪

11
00:01:13,536 --> 00:01:18,076
♪The wounds we've borne
are medals hidden within♪

12
00:01:18,336 --> 00:01:22,391
♪Standing alone on an open plain♪

13
00:01:23,168 --> 00:01:26,851
♪We gaze at the stars♪

14
00:01:31,228 --> 00:01:34,816
=The Dream Maker=

15
00:01:35,178 --> 00:01:37,912
=Episode 36=

16
00:01:39,436 --> 00:01:41,976
I was planning to sign the contract
with Yang Xiaohai tomorrow.

17
00:01:43,037 --> 00:01:43,757
What?

18
00:01:44,956 --> 00:01:47,236
Wang Lili has decided to go to Nanzhou.

19
00:01:49,236 --> 00:01:49,796
Why?

20
00:01:51,156 --> 00:01:52,837
Didn't you give her the blank contract?

21
00:01:53,037 --> 00:01:55,117
Did she make any outrageous demand?

22
00:01:56,356 --> 00:01:58,917
Not really. But Yuehai
can't meet her demand.

23
00:02:01,117 --> 00:02:01,677
Like what?

24
00:02:02,837 --> 00:02:04,117
A bigger stage.

25
00:02:07,076 --> 00:02:09,837
So she thinks Yuehai
isn't big and good enough.

26
00:02:12,517 --> 00:02:13,077
Maybe

27
00:02:14,716 --> 00:02:15,716
I'll go talk to her.

28
00:02:33,117 --> 00:02:35,476
Alright. Any other issues?

29
00:02:37,677 --> 00:02:39,317
If not, we'll

30
00:02:39,544 --> 00:02:40,957
listen to the mayor's hotline.

31
00:02:44,316 --> 00:02:46,797
Ms. Li, hello. I want to ask

32
00:02:47,316 --> 00:02:49,876
whether Yuehai can build
some star-rated hotels.

33
00:02:50,436 --> 00:02:53,716
Every time we receive important clients,
we can't arrange their accommodation.

34
00:02:54,876 --> 00:02:56,316
Forget about star-rated hotels,

35
00:02:56,916 --> 00:02:59,397
we don't even have space
to build regular hotels now.

36
00:02:59,837 --> 00:03:01,077
They all want land.

37
00:03:02,117 --> 00:03:03,277
There's not a plot left.

38
00:03:04,277 --> 00:03:04,920
Li.

39
00:03:05,592 --> 00:03:07,414
Write up a land-use application.

40
00:03:07,704 --> 00:03:08,677
Make it comprehensive.

41
00:03:09,237 --> 00:03:10,916
When I go
to the county office to report,

42
00:03:11,117 --> 00:03:12,636
I'll talk to Mr. Xia about it.

43
00:03:13,316 --> 00:03:13,716
Okay.

44
00:03:14,677 --> 00:03:15,517
Play the next one.

45
00:03:15,517 --> 00:03:16,036
Okay.

46
00:03:17,837 --> 00:03:19,916
Ms. Li, it's Wang Lili.

47
00:03:20,876 --> 00:03:23,237
I know you must be very sad
that I'm going to Nanzhou.

48
00:03:24,077 --> 00:03:26,168
But I'm not leaving
because Yuehai or you

49
00:03:26,584 --> 00:03:27,196
aren't good.

50
00:03:27,997 --> 00:03:29,077
But the world is big.

51
00:03:29,636 --> 00:03:31,117
I shouldn't just stay in Yuehai.

52
00:03:31,876 --> 00:03:34,077
You told me that I'm a genius.

53
00:03:34,756 --> 00:03:37,196
I deserve a better stage, don't I?

54
00:03:39,756 --> 00:03:40,344
Qiuping,

55
00:03:40,952 --> 00:03:43,397
I'd like to invite you to dinner tonight
at the Super Dog.

56
00:03:44,316 --> 00:03:45,916
Must come, okay?

57
00:03:46,997 --> 00:03:48,036
She is really something.

58
00:03:49,357 --> 00:03:50,997
She bullies Ms. Li and acts righteous.

59
00:03:51,436 --> 00:03:53,957
Exactly! This Wang Lili
is way out of line.

60
00:03:54,397 --> 00:03:56,117
Don't go! Why should you go?

61
00:03:56,756 --> 00:03:58,237
How dare she bullies Ms. Li.

62
00:03:58,557 --> 00:03:59,517
It's really outrageous.

63
00:04:01,397 --> 00:04:04,036
Ms. Li, don't take it to heart.

64
00:04:04,316 --> 00:04:06,117
Talented people
are always proud and insolent.

65
00:04:23,076 --> 00:04:25,516
Ms. Li, don't take it to heart.

66
00:04:25,557 --> 00:04:26,756
Life will teach her a lesson.

67
00:04:33,436 --> 00:04:33,876
Hello.

68
00:04:34,636 --> 00:04:36,037
Hello, Lili.

69
00:04:37,196 --> 00:04:37,797
Qiuping.

70
00:04:38,477 --> 00:04:39,797
I won't go to the Super Dog.

71
00:04:40,756 --> 00:04:42,117
But we still need to eat.

72
00:04:42,516 --> 00:04:43,480
Just come over.

73
00:04:43,946 --> 00:04:45,557
I'll treat you to a meal in our canteen.

74
00:04:47,357 --> 00:04:47,876
Okay.

75
00:04:52,316 --> 00:04:53,557
Meng, play the next one.

76
00:04:55,076 --> 00:04:55,477
Okay.

77
00:04:57,316 --> 00:04:58,597
Ms. Li, hello.

78
00:04:59,316 --> 00:05:01,516
I want to ask... Well...

79
00:05:01,677 --> 00:05:02,396
Thanks.

80
00:05:06,917 --> 00:05:07,316
Sit.

81
00:05:08,797 --> 00:05:10,756
Take a seat. Let's have a simple meal.

82
00:05:20,756 --> 00:05:21,316
Dive in.

83
00:05:38,328 --> 00:05:39,037
Have some soup.

84
00:05:52,597 --> 00:05:53,720
Did you change cooks?

85
00:05:54,357 --> 00:05:57,196
No. Same ones
as when you were attending night school.

86
00:06:00,088 --> 00:06:01,436
Maybe because you're leaving.

87
00:06:02,597 --> 00:06:03,956
I know I'm being quite selfish.

88
00:06:09,316 --> 00:06:11,477
But if I don't do this,
I'm afraid I'll regret it.

89
00:06:13,976 --> 00:06:15,117
I want to see the world.

90
00:06:18,157 --> 00:06:18,956
You told me,

91
00:06:20,196 --> 00:06:21,237
you are my lighthouse.

92
00:06:24,357 --> 00:06:25,117
I can do it.

93
00:06:28,677 --> 00:06:29,048
Lili.

94
00:06:30,008 --> 00:06:31,717
Nanzhou is a big city.

95
00:06:32,357 --> 00:06:34,076
With many people and fierce competition.

96
00:06:34,477 --> 00:06:36,157
You need to mentally prepare yourself.

97
00:06:36,597 --> 00:06:37,316
Definitely.

98
00:06:37,997 --> 00:06:39,032
But I believe

99
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:41,876
someone I value
will always have a bigger stage

100
00:06:43,157 --> 00:06:44,536
and shine just as brightly,

101
00:06:44,947 --> 00:06:46,956
no matter where they are.

102
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,797
I knew you'd understand me.

103
00:07:28,536 --> 00:07:29,717
Thank you.

104
00:07:32,756 --> 00:07:33,237
Lili,

105
00:07:34,477 --> 00:07:35,997
no matter where you go, never forget

106
00:07:37,876 --> 00:07:39,396
Yuehai is where you got your start.

107
00:07:40,536 --> 00:07:41,956
And Yuehai won't forget you.

108
00:08:34,676 --> 00:08:35,796
Do you like Wang Lili?

109
00:08:37,528 --> 00:08:38,036
Yes.

110
00:08:38,876 --> 00:08:39,957
I-I like her.

111
00:08:42,916 --> 00:08:43,796
She gave this to you.

112
00:08:45,144 --> 00:08:47,992
(Beautiful Sea)

113
00:08:58,072 --> 00:08:59,352
(Beautiful Sea)

114
00:09:01,317 --> 00:09:03,396
(Just letting you know,
we're a couple now.)

115
00:09:04,077 --> 00:09:06,597
(Here's a postcard for you
with both our names.)

116
00:09:07,237 --> 00:09:08,276
(Wait for your postcard.)

117
00:09:54,968 --> 00:09:55,928
Gosh!

118
00:09:57,396 --> 00:09:58,437
Trash!

119
00:10:00,636 --> 00:10:02,744
Who is it? No swearing
in the movie theater!

120
00:10:04,357 --> 00:10:06,136
Master, what are you doing here?

121
00:10:06,357 --> 00:10:07,036
Yang Xiaohai.

122
00:10:07,916 --> 00:10:09,437
Have you wasted all those skills

123
00:10:09,756 --> 00:10:11,437
you learned from me over the years?

124
00:10:11,756 --> 00:10:13,156
You didn't go to Guangzhou with me.

125
00:10:13,237 --> 00:10:15,512
You chose to go against me
and start a movie theater.

126
00:10:15,997 --> 00:10:17,592
Then do it properly.

127
00:10:17,592 --> 00:10:18,717
What kind of decor is this?

128
00:10:18,957 --> 00:10:20,440
This chair has even grown teeth.

129
00:10:21,368 --> 00:10:22,520
What's wrong, Master?

130
00:10:22,597 --> 00:10:24,117
It pinched my butt! How dare you ask!

131
00:10:24,597 --> 00:10:25,597
Master, let me tell you.

132
00:10:25,997 --> 00:10:28,077
Funds are limited right now.

133
00:10:28,477 --> 00:10:31,357
I have to prioritize getting these
essential infrastructure projects up.

134
00:10:31,636 --> 00:10:33,876
Things like chairs and tables
are secondhand ones.

135
00:10:34,156 --> 00:10:35,896
Just bear it. I'll upgrade step by step.

136
00:10:36,117 --> 00:10:38,317
You never listen to me,
and now you're paying.

137
00:10:38,556 --> 00:10:41,117
You can't make the movie theater thrive.

138
00:10:52,876 --> 00:10:55,237
Running a movie theater
is just like running a restaurant.

139
00:10:55,916 --> 00:10:57,676
Many people come and go
every single day.

140
00:10:58,077 --> 00:11:00,317
You have to please the majority

141
00:11:00,796 --> 00:11:01,636
to make it work.

142
00:11:02,516 --> 00:11:02,916
Got it.

143
00:11:03,556 --> 00:11:05,197
It's all about reputation and service.

144
00:11:06,077 --> 00:11:08,056
Look at this decor of yours
and those chairs.

145
00:11:08,248 --> 00:11:09,197
What's wrong?

146
00:11:09,528 --> 00:11:10,997
Within three days after opening,

147
00:11:11,117 --> 00:11:12,636
the chairs will pinch people's butts.

148
00:11:12,916 --> 00:11:13,836
With my light weight,

149
00:11:13,836 --> 00:11:14,876
it pinched me so hard.

150
00:11:15,237 --> 00:11:16,396
What about those heavier?

151
00:11:16,676 --> 00:11:18,040
Are you going to compensate them?

152
00:11:18,156 --> 00:11:19,237
How much will that cost?

153
00:11:20,357 --> 00:11:22,676
Step by step? Nobody's waiting for you.

154
00:11:23,317 --> 00:11:24,077
Absurd!

155
00:11:29,676 --> 00:11:30,366
Master.

156
00:11:30,936 --> 00:11:33,117
I know you don't want me
running a movie theater.

157
00:11:33,477 --> 00:11:35,197
But I've already rented the space.

158
00:11:35,396 --> 00:11:37,237
I have to make it work now.

159
00:11:37,516 --> 00:11:39,156
Yang Xiaohai,
where's your determination?

160
00:11:39,276 --> 00:11:40,796
Where's your determination?

161
00:11:41,237 --> 00:11:42,437
You're my only apprentice.

162
00:11:42,516 --> 00:11:43,544
If you embarrass me,

163
00:11:43,717 --> 00:11:44,916
how do I keep my reputation?

164
00:11:47,317 --> 00:11:48,472
Just about money, right?

165
00:11:48,856 --> 00:11:49,916
I'll become a shareholder.

166
00:11:52,477 --> 00:11:55,317
Master, opening a movie theater
is pretty risky.

167
00:11:55,477 --> 00:11:56,632
I can swallow the loss.

168
00:11:57,237 --> 00:11:59,676
I do it because I like it.

169
00:11:59,756 --> 00:12:01,796
But I don't want to drag you into this.

170
00:12:02,437 --> 00:12:03,717
Am I still your master?

171
00:12:04,156 --> 00:12:04,676
Yes.

172
00:12:05,117 --> 00:12:05,916
Then listen to me.

173
00:12:07,357 --> 00:12:08,597
Yang Xiaohai, listen up.

174
00:12:09,036 --> 00:12:10,117
You chose to go against me

175
00:12:10,636 --> 00:12:12,664
and run a movie theater,
so do it with conviction.

176
00:12:12,837 --> 00:12:14,168
Make it work.

177
00:12:14,357 --> 00:12:15,636
Make it successful, okay?

178
00:12:16,357 --> 00:12:16,837
Got it.

179
00:12:17,357 --> 00:12:18,516
Don't worry about me.

180
00:12:19,036 --> 00:12:21,756
I'm way more experienced
than you in making money.

181
00:12:22,396 --> 00:12:22,957
Got it?

182
00:12:25,156 --> 00:12:27,597
So what's next, Master?

183
00:12:28,276 --> 00:12:30,156
Next, you do nothing.

184
00:12:30,717 --> 00:12:32,876
Drop everything you're doing
and wait for my word.

185
00:12:36,077 --> 00:12:36,997
Have an egg tart.

186
00:12:37,636 --> 00:12:38,808
Here are toothpicks.

187
00:12:39,197 --> 00:12:39,992
Drink some tea.

188
00:12:39,992 --> 00:12:40,636
Thank you.

189
00:12:41,276 --> 00:12:41,676
Thank you.

190
00:12:43,717 --> 00:12:45,400
Said to hold the meeting at my company,

191
00:12:45,624 --> 00:12:46,756
but at Super Dog every time.

192
00:12:47,077 --> 00:12:48,437
Can we at least be professional?

193
00:12:49,036 --> 00:12:49,437
Xuemei.

194
00:12:50,117 --> 00:12:53,036
This counts as our chamber's
second conference room, right?

195
00:12:53,237 --> 00:12:54,796
Seems more like your second home.

196
00:12:55,276 --> 00:12:56,437
You're here every other day.

197
00:12:57,916 --> 00:13:00,312
By the way, about the parking spaces.

198
00:13:01,036 --> 00:13:02,706
More cars come to the industrial park,

199
00:13:02,706 --> 00:13:04,197
but they park messily,

200
00:13:04,317 --> 00:13:06,264
always blocking the firefighting access.

201
00:13:06,597 --> 00:13:08,248
I propose designating a parking zone

202
00:13:08,636 --> 00:13:10,360
in the industrial park.

203
00:13:10,796 --> 00:13:13,304
We register internal vehicles
and charge external ones.

204
00:13:13,756 --> 00:13:14,396
How's it?

205
00:13:14,837 --> 00:13:15,357
I agree.

206
00:13:15,448 --> 00:13:15,916
Agreed.

207
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:16,916
This works.

208
00:13:16,916 --> 00:13:18,197
Organized and profitable.

209
00:13:19,556 --> 00:13:20,317
That works.

210
00:13:24,636 --> 00:13:25,437
One more thing.

211
00:13:29,357 --> 00:13:31,576
That Yang Xiaohai,
Changyuan's apprentice,

212
00:13:32,117 --> 00:13:33,400
wants to open a movie theater.

213
00:13:33,837 --> 00:13:34,437
Xuemei.

214
00:13:34,876 --> 00:13:35,676
- Forget it.
- Yes.

215
00:13:35,756 --> 00:13:37,676
At first, I didn't think
it'd be profitable.

216
00:13:37,957 --> 00:13:40,477
But he is so motivated and determined.

217
00:13:40,957 --> 00:13:41,876
And I've been thinking

218
00:13:42,237 --> 00:13:44,156
more people are going
to cinemas these days.

219
00:13:44,597 --> 00:13:47,317
It's a small venture anyway.
A million yuan investment tops.

220
00:13:47,717 --> 00:13:50,597
I'll put in 100,000 yuan for one share.

221
00:13:50,997 --> 00:13:53,432
Anyone interested can sign up.

222
00:13:53,784 --> 00:13:54,317
Alright.

223
00:13:54,317 --> 00:13:54,676
Look.

224
00:13:54,676 --> 00:13:56,216
Xiaohai is my apprentice.

225
00:13:56,676 --> 00:13:58,276
For his startup,

226
00:13:58,317 --> 00:13:59,916
I could cover one million yuan myself.

227
00:14:00,117 --> 00:14:01,796
I didn't want to tell you.

228
00:14:02,077 --> 00:14:03,556
Later, Xuemei convinced me.

229
00:14:03,837 --> 00:14:05,837
Better to make money together.

230
00:14:06,237 --> 00:14:06,796
Well,

231
00:14:08,117 --> 00:14:10,156
100,000 yuan per person
for ten shares total.

232
00:14:10,516 --> 00:14:13,117
Completely voluntary.
I'll cover any shortfall.

233
00:14:13,556 --> 00:14:15,516
Xuemei, you're in for 100,000.

234
00:14:16,636 --> 00:14:17,357
I won.

235
00:14:18,317 --> 00:14:19,597
Full flush with all triplets.

236
00:14:21,556 --> 00:14:22,837
Ms. Gao, I'll get one share.

237
00:14:23,276 --> 00:14:23,597
Okay.

238
00:14:23,876 --> 00:14:24,556
One share, right?

239
00:14:25,237 --> 00:14:26,077
I'll record it.

240
00:14:26,276 --> 00:14:26,876
No, wait.

241
00:14:27,036 --> 00:14:29,077
Ten shares total
and each can only get one share.

242
00:14:29,237 --> 00:14:29,876
One per person.

243
00:14:30,077 --> 00:14:30,957
I'll take one.

244
00:14:31,237 --> 00:14:31,992
Okay, you're in.

245
00:14:32,197 --> 00:14:33,197
Then I'll get one too.

246
00:14:33,197 --> 00:14:34,237
- Hold on.
- Okay.

247
00:14:34,237 --> 00:14:34,636
I'm in.

248
00:14:34,796 --> 00:14:36,317
Fatty? Where's Fatty?

249
00:14:36,717 --> 00:14:37,756
Here! What's up?

250
00:14:37,876 --> 00:14:39,717
Fatty, play it for me.

251
00:14:39,756 --> 00:14:40,876
I'll go to the restroom.

252
00:14:41,036 --> 00:14:41,837
Mr. Guo.

253
00:14:42,357 --> 00:14:42,957
Aren't you in?

254
00:14:43,036 --> 00:14:43,556
Me?

255
00:14:44,197 --> 00:14:45,317
It's 100,000 yuan per share.

256
00:14:45,876 --> 00:14:48,237
100,000 yuan. I'll think about it.

257
00:14:48,437 --> 00:14:50,117
100,000 yuan, ten people.

258
00:14:50,357 --> 00:14:52,237
Perfect in every way. How great.

259
00:14:52,676 --> 00:14:53,997
Don't be such a killjoy.

260
00:14:59,416 --> 00:15:01,837
Alright, count me in for one share.

261
00:15:02,156 --> 00:15:02,916
I'll record it.

262
00:15:03,032 --> 00:15:03,717
Good.

263
00:15:04,437 --> 00:15:05,396
Come on.

264
00:15:11,477 --> 00:15:14,117
Attention, here's an announcement.

265
00:15:14,837 --> 00:15:16,837
(Yuehai Town's first movie theater,)

266
00:15:17,117 --> 00:15:19,636
(Quanmei Cinema)
(Quanmei Cinema, is finally open!)

267
00:15:20,237 --> 00:15:21,797
(Ten shareholders of the movie theater)

268
00:15:21,797 --> 00:15:23,357
(invite all the residents for movies.)

269
00:15:24,317 --> 00:15:25,796
(Free admission on opening day.)

270
00:15:26,477 --> 00:15:28,717
(Seats are limited.
First come, first served.)

271
00:15:28,717 --> 00:15:29,317
(Grand Opening of Quanmei Cinema)

272
00:15:29,317 --> 00:15:30,437
Welcome!

273
00:15:30,837 --> 00:15:31,437
Welcome!

274
00:15:31,437 --> 00:15:32,317
- All here?
- All here.

275
00:15:32,477 --> 00:15:33,396
Congratulations!

