I'm finding it hard to believe you.

564
00:27:29,116 --> 00:27:30,136
It's true.

565
00:27:30,392 --> 00:27:32,197
He's going to propose to Yan today.

566
00:27:33,237 --> 00:27:33,756
No way.

567
00:27:34,516 --> 00:27:35,516
Why not?

568
00:27:35,917 --> 00:27:38,477
He ordered 999 roses
at the flower market.

569
00:27:39,157 --> 00:27:41,076
999 roses. What does that mean?

570
00:27:41,637 --> 00:27:42,796
Definitely for a proposal.

571
00:27:43,637 --> 00:27:44,036
Well...

572
00:27:44,717 --> 00:27:47,556
What could the two of us even do there?

573
00:27:48,076 --> 00:27:49,316
We're going to site install.

574
00:27:50,437 --> 00:27:50,957
Master.

575
00:27:51,556 --> 00:27:52,236
Tonight,

576
00:27:52,792 --> 00:27:55,197
let's double-check the details
on the construction drawing.

577
00:27:56,397 --> 00:27:56,997
Okay.

578
00:27:59,157 --> 00:27:59,637
You!

579
00:27:59,637 --> 00:28:01,076
- Did he hear it?
- Clean that up.

580
00:28:02,076 --> 00:28:02,637
Master.

581
00:28:04,836 --> 00:28:05,556
Master.

582
00:28:09,036 --> 00:28:09,556
Master.

583
00:28:13,076 --> 00:28:14,997
Master, he's going to propose.

584
00:28:15,157 --> 00:28:16,216
You're still not going?

585
00:28:16,216 --> 00:28:17,556
Wait, it's not my business.

586
00:28:18,796 --> 00:28:21,596
Master, you never give up on Ms. Sun.

587
00:28:21,796 --> 00:28:23,197
Why do you have to deny it?

588
00:28:23,356 --> 00:28:23,877
He...

589
00:28:28,516 --> 00:28:29,877
If he really proposes today,

590
00:28:29,912 --> 00:28:31,157
you'd only regret it.

591
00:28:31,356 --> 00:28:32,717
What would I regret?

592
00:28:33,316 --> 00:28:34,917
She runs this kind of karaoke bar,

593
00:28:34,997 --> 00:28:36,877
probably just wanting
to meet some big shot.

594
00:28:37,397 --> 00:28:38,356
Now she made it.

595
00:28:39,917 --> 00:28:41,116
I wish her all the best.

596
00:28:42,997 --> 00:28:44,157
Wait, Master.

597
00:28:44,437 --> 00:28:47,397
Yuehai has over 20 karaoke bars
and a dozen dance halls now.

598
00:28:47,477 --> 00:28:49,516
Hundreds of people
visit these places every day.

599
00:28:49,957 --> 00:28:51,276
Does it mean they're all indecent

600
00:28:51,596 --> 00:28:52,596
and dubious?

601
00:28:56,596 --> 00:28:57,556
Then I'm indecent.

602
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:05,677
(Yan Dance Hall)

603
00:29:05,677 --> 00:29:06,437
Sir, want to sing?

604
00:29:07,237 --> 00:29:07,836
Come on in.

605
00:29:08,036 --> 00:29:09,116
Is singing free here?

606
00:29:09,796 --> 00:29:10,437
Yes.

607
00:29:12,408 --> 00:29:17,272
(Yan Dance Hall)

608
00:29:18,957 --> 00:29:19,437
Take care.

609
00:29:24,312 --> 00:29:25,036
(Yan Dance Hall)

610
00:29:25,036 --> 00:29:26,717
Sir, someone paid the bills tonight.

611
00:29:26,836 --> 00:29:28,917
Singing and drinks for free.
Want to come and try?

612
00:29:31,677 --> 00:29:32,397
Go on in.

613
00:29:32,796 --> 00:29:33,197
No.

614
00:29:41,516 --> 00:29:42,116
Yan.

615
00:29:42,997 --> 00:29:44,397
Yan.

616
00:29:47,836 --> 00:29:49,596
What do I do to earn your forgiveness?

617
00:29:50,717 --> 00:29:52,197
I stopped hating you long ago.

618
00:29:53,437 --> 00:29:54,957
But I've been here over half a month,

619
00:29:55,877 --> 00:29:57,197
yet you won't even sing with me.

620
00:29:57,477 --> 00:29:59,877
I made myself very clear from day one.

621
00:30:00,917 --> 00:30:03,116
I run a business
and I won't kick you out.

622
00:30:04,076 --> 00:30:05,677
But I'm not part of the business deal.

623
00:30:05,997 --> 00:30:07,637
I never thought that way.

624
00:30:08,356 --> 00:30:09,556
I just want it like before,

625
00:30:10,036 --> 00:30:11,437
the two of us singing together.

626
00:30:12,197 --> 00:30:15,076
You have everything now.
You can find someone else to sing with.

627
00:30:18,836 --> 00:30:19,596
All these years,

628
00:30:20,756 --> 00:30:21,848
I found out I...

629
00:30:22,808 --> 00:30:24,796
I only love you.

630
00:30:27,276 --> 00:30:27,957
Besides,

631
00:30:29,197 --> 00:30:30,276
we have a child.

632
00:30:31,356 --> 00:30:33,917
Stop throwing a temper. Come back
to Shanghai with me, okay?

633
00:30:36,397 --> 00:30:36,877
Right.

634
00:30:38,957 --> 00:30:40,157
You are Haohao's father.

635
00:30:40,957 --> 00:30:42,836
That's something I can never change.

636
00:30:43,316 --> 00:30:46,237
This time,
I absolutely won't let you down.

637
00:30:46,237 --> 00:30:49,944
(Yan Dance Hall)

638
00:30:50,516 --> 00:30:51,316
I'm not worried.

639
00:30:52,677 --> 00:30:54,556
You won't get a chance
to let me down anyway.

640
00:30:56,076 --> 00:30:58,516
We broke up long ago.

641
00:30:59,397 --> 00:31:01,076
Breakup means ending.

642
00:31:01,756 --> 00:31:03,064
I don't know how you feel,

643
00:31:03,064 --> 00:31:05,752
but for me, people need to look forward

644
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:07,596
and never look back.

645
00:31:09,116 --> 00:31:11,637
Even if you are my child's father,

646
00:31:11,997 --> 00:31:13,477
you can't make me look back.

647
00:31:52,516 --> 00:31:52,957
What's up?

648
00:31:54,116 --> 00:31:56,146
Heard a big boss wants to propose to me

649
00:31:56,344 --> 00:31:57,304
and came to bless me?

650
00:32:00,237 --> 00:32:01,437
Then you're here for the show.

651
00:32:07,276 --> 00:32:07,836
Yan.

652
00:32:09,556 --> 00:32:10,157
I'm sorry.

653
00:32:12,836 --> 00:32:13,516
In the past,

654
00:32:15,036 --> 00:32:16,637
I just didn't understand you.

655
00:32:19,917 --> 00:32:20,477
It's over now.

656
00:32:22,116 --> 00:32:23,076
We need to look forward.

657
00:32:26,677 --> 00:32:28,036
Since you're here, come in.

658
00:32:32,756 --> 00:32:33,556
Maybe next time.

659
00:32:33,997 --> 00:32:35,576
This singing thing, I...

660
00:32:36,088 --> 00:32:37,197
I need to practice more.

661
00:32:39,796 --> 00:32:40,316
Right.

662
00:32:40,997 --> 00:32:41,997
When I'm not working,

663
00:32:43,316 --> 00:32:44,836
I should learn something.

664
00:32:47,316 --> 00:32:47,796
Okay.

665
00:32:50,397 --> 00:32:52,316
I think we can still be friends, right?

666
00:32:58,596 --> 00:33:00,677
You go practice. Come back anytime.

667
00:33:01,116 --> 00:33:02,437
You can enjoy free service here.

668
00:33:05,368 --> 00:33:07,832
♪You came quietly♪

669
00:33:09,624 --> 00:33:12,358
♪And left quietly♪

670
00:33:14,232 --> 00:33:16,280
♪Perhaps one day♪

671
00:33:16,536 --> 00:33:18,634
♪It won't really matter♪

672
00:33:18,648 --> 00:33:21,368
♪Who will still remember♪

673
00:33:22,776 --> 00:33:25,304
♪You and me♪

674
00:33:27,576 --> 00:33:29,624
♪You are a beam of light♪

675
00:33:29,624 --> 00:33:32,088
(Yan Dance Hall)
♪In dazzling years♪

676
00:33:32,088 --> 00:33:35,544
(Yan Dance Hall)
♪Shining on me alone in the dark♪

677
00:33:36,536 --> 00:33:38,552
♪You are a boat♪

678
00:33:38,552 --> 00:33:40,824
♪Carrying our dreams♪

679
00:33:40,824 --> 00:33:43,960
♪Braving the wind and waves
towards the light♪

680
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:45,951
(Celebrating the 3rd Anniversary
of Yuehai Printing Industrial Park)

681
00:33:46,116 --> 00:33:46,637
Nice.

682
00:33:47,157 --> 00:33:47,596
Ms. Gao.

683
00:33:48,356 --> 00:33:50,957
Your machines and equipment here
are quite advanced.

684
00:33:51,157 --> 00:33:51,596
Right.

685
00:33:51,957 --> 00:33:54,357
They're much advanced than
those state-owned factories

686
00:33:54,552 --> 00:33:55,356
in the county.

687
00:33:55,796 --> 00:33:57,677
Mr. Xia, not just them.

688
00:33:58,036 --> 00:33:59,756
Even the big printeries in the city

689
00:33:59,796 --> 00:34:00,957
can't compare to ours.

690
00:34:01,276 --> 00:34:02,957
This year, we imported a brand-new

691
00:34:03,076 --> 00:34:05,197
Heidelberg four-color printing press.

692
00:34:05,717 --> 00:34:08,437
It's currently the most advanced press
on the market.

693
00:34:08,676 --> 00:34:09,196
Really?

694
00:34:09,357 --> 00:34:10,236
Take a look over here.

695
00:34:10,236 --> 00:34:10,797
Okay.

696
00:34:10,797 --> 00:34:11,957
(Actively Develop the Printing Industry,
Boost Yuehai's Economic Growth)

697
00:34:11,957 --> 00:34:14,156
Here. We've prepared some snacks.

698
00:34:14,357 --> 00:34:15,277
Please enjoy.

699
00:34:15,636 --> 00:34:16,196
Gao.

700
00:34:16,797 --> 00:34:18,957
About those imported machines
you mentioned,

701
00:34:19,076 --> 00:34:21,076
do any of our workers
know how to operate them?

702
00:34:21,636 --> 00:34:23,917
Mr. Guan, a few years back,
we started a night school.

703
00:34:24,116 --> 00:34:25,720
Besides teaching them
cultural knowledge,

704
00:34:25,917 --> 00:34:28,477
we also trained them
into modern workers.

705
00:34:28,797 --> 00:34:30,196
- Yes.
- Good.

706
00:34:30,516 --> 00:34:32,676
So how many such industrial parks
does Yuehai have?

707
00:34:33,196 --> 00:34:35,384
We'd like to build a few more.

708
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,437
But...

709
00:34:37,877 --> 00:34:39,757
Guan, you get that?

710
00:34:40,156 --> 00:34:43,076
Sit. They didn't invite us
for a tour for nothing.

711
00:34:43,596 --> 00:34:45,556
But I'll be honest,

712
00:34:45,912 --> 00:34:48,376
you can build anything,
but the county government lacks money.

713
00:34:52,397 --> 00:34:53,437
Mr. Xia,

714
00:34:54,196 --> 00:34:56,196
you've misunderstood.
We're not short on money,

715
00:34:56,757 --> 00:34:58,357
but short on land.

716
00:34:59,236 --> 00:35:00,997
We have no plot of land
to build anything.

717
00:35:01,357 --> 00:35:04,116
We have the funds and investment,

718
00:35:04,676 --> 00:35:06,957
but with no land.

719
00:35:08,036 --> 00:35:08,556
Exactly.

720
00:35:12,036 --> 00:35:12,596
Xia.

721
00:35:13,716 --> 00:35:15,636
Yuehai's development is so fast.

722
00:35:15,917 --> 00:35:17,112
The county government should

723
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:19,156
try harder to support them.

724
00:35:19,957 --> 00:35:21,676
Guan, I have considered it.

725
00:35:22,076 --> 00:35:23,757
But the task is just too difficult.

726
00:35:24,236 --> 00:35:24,877
You know,

727
00:35:25,716 --> 00:35:27,797
the county government
has been giving Yuehai

728
00:35:28,236 --> 00:35:29,757
policy advantages all these years.

729
00:35:30,036 --> 00:35:32,036
If we ask other towns for land,

730
00:35:32,156 --> 00:35:33,477
it'll be too difficult.

731
00:35:34,477 --> 00:35:37,076
But I think you understand it, right?

732
00:35:38,797 --> 00:35:39,377
Yuehai

733
00:35:39,544 --> 00:35:41,917
is the leader of Pingchuan's economy

734
00:35:42,636 --> 00:35:44,676
and has been racing ahead
all these years.

735
00:35:45,357 --> 00:35:47,596
Of course, we have to support you.

736
00:35:49,317 --> 00:35:49,752
Well,

737
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:52,596
we'll discuss this
at the meeting next Monday.

738
00:35:55,156 --> 00:35:56,156
That'd be fantastic!

739
00:35:56,516 --> 00:35:58,596
Thank you, Mr. Xia. Thank you, Mr. Guan.

740
00:36:01,076 --> 00:36:02,757
By the way, I heard

741
00:36:03,076 --> 00:36:04,837
a new movie theater opened in Yuehai.

742
00:36:05,277 --> 00:36:05,816
Yes.

743
00:36:06,008 --> 00:36:08,676
Ms. Gao and other partners opened it.

744
00:36:08,716 --> 00:36:09,277
Right.

745
00:36:09,877 --> 00:36:11,596
- There are...
- Ten shareholders total.

746
00:36:12,156 --> 00:36:13,716
Self-employed individuals in Yuehai.

747
00:36:14,317 --> 00:36:15,556
The movie theater is bustling.

748
00:36:15,797 --> 00:36:18,556
They show not just new releases
but many classic movies too.

749
00:36:18,716 --> 00:36:19,288
Really?

750
00:36:19,576 --> 00:36:21,837
Neither Mr. Zheng nor I
have been there yet.

751
00:36:21,997 --> 00:36:23,437
- Really?
- We haven't had the time.

752
00:36:23,556 --> 00:36:24,516
I love classic movies,

753
00:36:24,636 --> 00:36:25,944
especially black-and-white ones.

754
00:36:26,236 --> 00:36:27,000
Perfect!

755
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:29,116
After dinner, let's all go watch one.

756
00:36:29,277 --> 00:36:29,837
Okay.

757
00:36:29,917 --> 00:36:30,716
Wonderful!

758
00:36:31,156 --> 00:36:32,076
Welcome.

759
00:36:37,076 --> 00:36:38,477
(Don't move.)

760
00:36:39,076 --> 00:36:40,556
(You're probably just overexcited.)

761
00:36:40,997 --> 00:36:42,116
Find any seat.

762
00:36:42,357 --> 00:36:43,357
Here. Sit here.

763
00:36:43,397 --> 00:36:44,036
Sit here.

764
00:36:44,317 --> 00:36:45,797
The middle seats are best.

765
00:36:47,116 --> 00:36:47,556
Sit.

766
00:36:47,596 --> 00:36:48,156
Here.

767
00:36:48,156 --> 00:36:48,716
Alright.

768
00:36:48,757 --> 00:36:49,397
Thanks.

769
00:36:49,397 --> 00:36:50,757
(I told you not to move.)

770
00:36:51,156 --> 00:36:52,997
(You really are something.)

771
00:36:53,357 --> 00:36:56,036
(I've told you,
I get off at Xiaoqiao Station too.)

772
00:36:56,556 --> 00:36:57,317
Not bad.

773
00:36:57,397 --> 00:36:59,676
- (I won't lose you.)
- (That station is nice, right?)

774
00:36:59,917 --> 00:37:00,676
Seen it before?

775
00:37:01,317 --> 00:37:01,957
No.

776
00:37:02,797 --> 00:37:03,556
Me neither.

777
00:37:03,556 --> 00:37:05,877
(Never had an accident.
Station is so tidy.)

778
00:37:06,757 --> 00:37:09,196
(Miss, can you sit here?)

779
00:37:09,477 --> 00:37:11,477
(His head keeps bobbing
like a wind-up toy.)

780
00:37:11,636 --> 00:37:13,797
(I-I can't start sketching.)

781
00:37:16,196 --> 00:37:17,236
No, thanks.

782
00:37:20,317 --> 00:37:22,477
I don't like this stuff, either.
You have it.

783
00:37:22,757 --> 00:37:25,477
(Mr. Painter, I have a special request.)

784
00:37:25,957 --> 00:37:26,636
(Special?)

785
00:37:26,837 --> 00:37:29,636
(Could you paint me
wearing peasant attire?)

786
00:37:30,036 --> 00:37:30,837
(Why?)

787
00:37:31,236 --> 00:37:34,116
(To learn from the working people
and show my resolve to be tempered.)

788
00:37:34,676 --> 00:37:36,757
Cigarettes, pastries, sausage.

789
00:37:37,236 --> 00:37:39,636
Cigarettes, pastries, sausage.

790
00:37:40,036 --> 00:37:42,477
Peanuts, sunflower seeds, candies.

791
00:37:42,797 --> 00:37:44,716
Cigarettes, pastries, sausage.

792
00:37:44,837 --> 00:37:47,236
How could you sell
things and snacks in here?

793
00:37:47,437 --> 00:37:48,196
It's a quiet place.

794
00:37:49,556 --> 00:37:50,957
Can't watch with no snacks.

795
00:37:51,236 --> 00:37:52,837
Can't watch with no drinks.

796
00:37:53,357 --> 00:37:54,236
Want some?

797
00:37:54,676 --> 00:37:55,556
Keep it down.

798
00:37:56,116 --> 00:37:57,397
Keep it down. Just push it away.

799
00:37:57,437 --> 00:37:58,076
Push it away.

800
00:37:58,196 --> 00:37:59,437
Don't disturb others watching.

801
00:37:59,516 --> 00:38:00,797
No more selling here.

802
00:38:01,437 --> 00:38:01,797
Okay.

803
00:38:01,877 --> 00:38:02,917
I'll tell him later.

804
00:38:02,997 --> 00:38:03,596
Right.

805
00:38:04,957 --> 00:38:06,477
How can they sell stuff here?

806
00:38:06,757 --> 00:38:07,516
(Take care.)

807
00:38:07,917 --> 00:38:09,036
(See you later.)

808
00:38:12,696 --> 00:38:14,744
(Mr. Painter, I'll be right back.
Continue then.)

809
00:38:14,744 --> 00:38:15,277
(Okay.)

810
00:38:15,556 --> 00:38:17,156
(That young man is really enthusiastic.)

811
00:38:19,556 --> 00:38:22,317
Li, Decheng,
do you two hear splashing water?

812
00:38:23,036 --> 00:38:23,716
Splashing water?

813
00:38:24,596 --> 00:38:25,196
Didn't hear it.

814
00:38:25,716 --> 00:38:26,156
Ouch!

815
00:38:26,837 --> 00:38:27,397
Feels good.

816
00:38:28,076 --> 00:38:28,957
What's going on there?

817
00:38:31,196 --> 00:38:32,556
Mr. Xia, I'll go ask.

818
00:38:33,596 --> 00:38:34,437
What's going on?

819
00:38:34,837 --> 00:38:35,477
Take it.

820
00:38:39,437 --> 00:38:41,196
Well, what are you doing?

821
00:38:41,516 --> 00:38:42,196
Foot massage?

822
00:38:42,317 --> 00:38:44,596
Two people ahead. Need to wait an hour.

823
00:38:46,036 --> 00:38:47,676
Why are they getting foot massages here?

824
00:38:48,076 --> 00:38:49,116
What are you doing here?

825
00:38:49,477 --> 00:38:51,277
- This is the movie theater.
- Hush! Quiet!

826
00:38:52,636 --> 00:38:54,036
Mr. Xia, please have a seat.

827
00:38:54,317 --> 00:38:55,917
Don't worry. I'll go ask.

828
00:38:57,036 --> 00:38:57,976
- Sit down.
- I'll go ask.

829
00:38:58,712 --> 00:38:59,556
Go ahead.

830
00:39:04,716 --> 00:39:05,277
Xiaohai.

831
00:39:06,156 --> 00:39:06,757
Ms. Li.

832
00:39:07,437 --> 00:39:08,556
What's going on inside?

833
00:39:08,797 --> 00:39:10,716
Why are there foot massages?
What a mess!

834
00:39:11,837 --> 00:39:14,156
Master said selling tickets
doesn't make money,

835
00:39:14,636 --> 00:39:16,397
so we offer unique services.

836
00:39:16,797 --> 00:39:17,837
This is outrageous!

837
00:39:18,156 --> 00:39:20,036
Right, I argued with him too.

838
00:39:20,317 --> 00:39:21,317
But I hold a small share.

